system.description: When you act clueless, goofy, or confused to get out of a sticky mundane situation, roll + Freak.

failure.label: Complications...
failure.value: No one is fooled, and you’ve put yourself in their crosshairs.

partial.label: Partial success
partial.value: You create an opportunity, a distraction, or a plausible excuse. You also feel all the weight of playing the clown and of the people staring at you. The GM shifts one of your Labels up and one down.

success.label: Success!
success.value: You create an opportunity, a distraction, or a plausible excuse.
